<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { 
        title: 'Comedor de los Pobres - Juárez', 
        description: 'Conoce el Comedor Juan XXIII en Juárez, N.L. Brindamos alimento y esperanza a quienes más lo necesitan.' 
    }) %>
    <style>
        :root {
            --morado: #7c3aed;
            --amarillo: #fbbf24;
            --naranja: #f97316;
        }

        /* Hero Ultra Moderno */
        .hero-visual {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c27bf8 0%, #946ed6 100%);
            min-height: 70vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-pattern {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            opacity: 0.1;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#ffffff 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
        }

        .hero-image-card {
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(-15deg) rotateX(5deg);
            box-shadow: -20px 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .hero-image-card:hover {
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(0deg) rotateX(0deg);
        }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            grid-auto-rows: 240px;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .gallery-item:nth-child(2) { grid-column: span 2; }
        .gallery-item:nth-child(3) { grid-row: span 2; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-auto-rows: 250px; }
            .gallery-item { grid-column: span 1 !important; grid-row: span 1 !important; }
            .hero-image-card { transform: none; }
        }

        .accent-border {
            border-left: 6px solid var(--naranja);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-800">

    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero-visual text-white">
        <div class="hero-pattern"></div>
        
        <!-- Círculos decorativos -->
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-yellow-400/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-none mb-6">
                    Sede <br>
                    <span id="sede-titulo" class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-500">Juarez</span>
                </h1>
                <p id="sede-subtitulo" class="text-xl text-purple-100 max-w-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                    Sirviendo con amor y dignidad en el corazón de Nuevo León.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="hidden lg:block">
                <div class="hero-image-card rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden border-4 border-white/20">
                    <img id="sede-hero-img" src="/imagenes/Comedor Juarez/CJ.1.jpg" alt="Comedor" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Información de Sede -->
    <section class="py-24">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-20">
                
                <!-- Contenido Dinámico -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                    <div class="accent-border pl-8 mb-12">
                        <span class="text-orange-500 font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Información General</span>
                        <h2 id="sede-nombre-completo" class="text-4xl font-black text-purple-900 mt-2">Comedor Juarez</h2>
                    </div>

                    <div id="sede-descripcion" class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>El Comedor Unidad Juárez nace de un trabajo en conjunto con la Secretaría de Igualdad e Inclusión, con el objetivo de disminuir el hambre a partir de una nutrición adecuada.</p>
                        <p>Abre sus puertas un espacio digno para atender a cientos de personas de las colonias aledañas, sirviendo un plato de comida diariamente a niños, jóvenes, adultos y personas de la tercera edad.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Stats Rápidos -->
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-10">
                        <div class="p-6 bg-purple-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart text-purple-600 mb-3 text-xl"></i>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">Impacto</p>
                            <p class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">Comunitario</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-orange-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mb-3 text-xl"></i>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">Servicio</p>
                            <p class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">Lun-Sab</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-yellow-50 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-yellow-500 mb-3 text-xl"></i>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">Apoyo</p>
                            <p class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">Gratuito</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Datos de contacto / Ubicación -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-5">
                    <div class="sticky top-10">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-[3rem] p-10 shadow-2xl shadow-purple-900/10 border border-purple-50">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-purple-900 mb-8 flex items-center">
                                <span class="w-2 h-8 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full mr-4"></span>
                                ¿Cómo llegar?
                            </h3>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-8">
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-5">
                                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 flex-shrink-0">
                                        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-xl"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Dirección</p>
                                        <p id="sede-direccion" class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Calle Lomas de Francia s/n (entre Lomas de México y Lomas de Ecuador), Colonia Arboledas de los Naranjos, Juárez, N.L. C.P. 67288</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden h-48 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 relative">
                                    <iframe 
                                        src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Centro+Comunitario+Arboledas+de+los+Naranjos+Juárez+Nuevo+León&hl=es&z=17&output=embed" 
                                        class="w-full h-full border-0 absolute inset-0" 
                                        allowfullscreen="" 
                                        loading="lazy" 
                                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                                    </iframe>
                                </div>

                                <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Centro+Comunitario+Arboledas+de+los+Naranjos+Juárez+Nuevo+León" target="_blank" class="block w-full py-5 bg-purple-600 text-white text-center font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-purple-700 transition shadow-xl shadow-purple-200 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm cursor-pointer">
                                    Ver en Navegador
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Galería (Sin botón de ver más) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-purple-900">Nuestra Labor</h2>
                <div class="h-1 flex-grow mx-8 bg-gray-200 rounded-full hidden md:block"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="gallery-grid">
               
                <div class="gallery-item rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg group">
                    <img src="/imagenes/Comedor Juarez/CJ.1.jpg" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg group">
                    <img src="/imagenes/Comedor Juarez/CJ.2.jpg" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
                </div>
                
                <div class="gallery-item rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg group">
                    <img src="/imagenes/Comedor Juarez/CJ.3.jpg" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg group">
                    <img src="/imagenes/Comedor Juarez/CJ.4.jpg" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>